{
  "stem": "21582.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Can you tell me about the-- the formation of the ghetto and the building of the wall?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The formation of the ghetto-- in a way-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the formation of the ghetto, in a way, occurred right away, because you were-- I think the wall was the most visible and the most tangible and the most-- I mean, you can point at it even today.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I doubt that there is any piece left, but that is very easy to imagine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But actually, the formation of the ghetto started the minute the Germans came in, the minute they marched in, because you were immediately identified.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- immediately certain streets were forbidden for Jews and certain streets were designated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So even though there was not a wall, of course, the wall marked it off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't recall when they started the wall, whether it was in '41.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it was in '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that to us, also it did make an impression, because right around the walls, you had the Germans stationed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the-- the fact that we were so boxed in became much more-- much more visible to us, not that we didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, we were afraid to come too close to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, then also getting-- getting through for some people to either go there for hiding.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or-- you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] or to go there for food, also became much more difficult, because it was harder to get through.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that there was some Polish guards, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know that the Germans enlisted the help of Lithuanians and Ukrainians, and I think-- and Poles.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
